Package: knhanesget
Title: 安装和更新 knhanes
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Heng", family = "Liu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lh1399780@163.com")
Description: Provides a lightweight public installer for knhanes. It creates
    a random installation request code compatible with knhanes, downloads and
    verifies versioned release archives, and supports activation, version
    checks, updates, and local deactivation. It contains no KNHANES data,
    knhanes analysis code, GitHub access token, or private signing key.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    curl,
    jsonlite,
    sodium,
    tibble
Suggests:
    knhanes,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
